title: StarTalk Live: I, Robot (Part 1)
description: From Mars to Europa, the human exploration of space is increasingly robotic. Laugh and learn about our mechanical marvels from Neil deGrasse Tyson, Eugene Mirman and their special guests at StarTalk Live.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
